text: Palo Pinto is a census-designated place and unincorporated community and county seat in Palo Pinto County, Texas, United States. In 2020, 276 people lived there. This was a new CDP for the 2010 census. ==References== Category:Census-designated places in Texas Category:Unincorporated communities in Texas Category:County seats in Texas
title: Palo Pinto, Texas
